'''热带风暴格雷斯'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Grace}}）是[[2009年大西洋飓风季|2009年大西洋飓风季]]期间第七场获得命名的风暴，也是有纪录以来形成位置最偏东北方向的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]<ref name="TCR">{{cite report | author = Robbie Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-11-28 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Tropical Cyclone Report | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL092009_Grace.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304124800/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL092009_Grace.pdf | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。系统于10月4日经[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]上空的[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]发展形成，然后逐渐增强至[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时100公里的最高强度并发展出[[风眼|眼状特征]]，但由于行经海域[[海面温度|水温]]偏低，中心附近的[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动发展受限。10月6日，格雷斯失去热带天气系统特征，其残留最终同[[不列颠群岛|不列颠群岛]]附近的另一个天气系统融合。

这场风暴对陆地的影响很小，途经亚速尔群岛期间，部分离气旋中心较近的岛屿测得的风速达到每小时71公里，还出现中等程度降水。受格雷斯及其它因素的共同影响，葡萄牙降下暴雨，导致部分街道被淹。风暴残留之后还对爱尔兰和英国部分地区构成影响，当地测得约51毫米雨量和热带风暴强度大风，但没有造成破坏。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Grace 2009 track.png}}
热带风暴格雷斯源自9月27日[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]][[瑞斯角_(纽芬兰岛)|瑞斯角]]（{{lang|en|Cape Race}}）以东约755公里海域一股[[冷锋|冷锋]]沿线形成的大规模[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]<ref name="TCR" />。系统起初同[[锢囚锋|锢囚锋]]相联，低气压区脱离后逐渐呈现出热带天气系统特征<ref name="D1">{{cite report | author1 = Daniel Brown | author2 = James Franklin | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Discussion One | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304124800/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/AL092009_Grace.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.001.shtml? }}</ref><ref name="JeffM">{{cite web | author = Jeff Masters | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Surprise tropical storm forms near the Azores; Invest 91L has potential to develop | archivedate = 2015-11-05 | deadurl = yes | url = https://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=1340&tstamp= | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151105164243/http://www.wunderground.com/blog/JeffMasters/comment.html?entrynum=1340&tstamp= }}</ref>。到10月1日时系统行经亚速尔群岛中部时，其中心附近已开始发展出降雨和雷暴活动<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-01 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook}}</ref>。但到了第二天，系统关联的[[对流|对流]]却又开始消退<ref>{{cite report | author = Jack Beven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-02 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook}}</ref>，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]因此停止监控<ref>{{cite report | author1 = David Roberts | author2 = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-02 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook}}</ref>。接下来两天里，系统在亚速尔群岛附近的移动路线形成逆时针环路。10月4日下午，低气压区中心周围重新发展出对流<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel Brown | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-04 | title = Tropical Weather Outlook}}</ref>，因此在[[圣米格尔岛|圣米格尔岛]]附近升级成热带风暴<ref name="TCR" />。不过，美国国家飓风中心在系统已成为热带气旋后的连续数小时里都没有发布公告<ref name="D1" />。

美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]10月4日下午15点发布针对气旋的首份公告，风暴获名“格雷斯”（{{lang|en|Grace}}），成为[[2009年大西洋飓风季|2009年大西洋飓风季]]第七场获得命名的风暴。气旋的对流相对较强，围绕[[风眼|眼状特征]]旋转。虽然格雷斯行经洋面的[[海面温度|水温]]通常来说不足以支撑热带气旋发展，但由于[[风切变|风切变]]很少，其对流依然得以持续。受西北大西洋上空的南向气流影响，风暴朝西北方向稳步前进。<ref name="D1" />虽然行经洋面水温逐渐降低，但气旋还是有小幅强化<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd Kimberlain | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304212103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.002.shtml | title = Tropical Storm Grace Discussion Two | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.002.shtml? | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，估计其风速于10月5日清晨达到每小时100公里<ref name="TCR" />。

受附近的大范围[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]影响，格雷斯的结构开始退化，对流逐渐减弱并且变得不对称。风暴此时所在海域水温仅有18摄氏度，这样的温度通常无法支撑对流发展。<ref>{{cite report | author = Robbie Berg | publisher = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Discussion Three | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205133/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.003.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.003.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。10月5日，风暴中的降雨和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动持续消退，但仍然保持着深层暖芯这一标志性热带天气系统特征<ref>{{cite report | author = Michael Brennan | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Discussion Four | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304193519/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.004.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.004.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。10月6日清晨，美国国家飓风中心发布针对格雷斯的最后一份公告，称气旋已同东北大西洋上空的[[锋_(气象)|锋面天气系统]]融合，风暴关联的最低[[气压|气压]]也是在这次融合前不久测得，低至986[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.12[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）<ref>{{cite report | author = Daniel Brown | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2009-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Tropical Storm Grace Discussion Five (Final) | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304222638/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.005.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2009/al09/al092009.discus.005.shtml? | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。格雷斯的温带残留接下来又持续了约18小时，最终于10月7日清晨在[[凯尔特海|凯尔特海]]上空消散<ref name="TCR" />。不过，[[美国海军研究实验室|美国海军研究实验室]]还在继续监控，直至数小时后系统进入[[北海_(大西洋)|北海]]上空为止<ref>{{cite report |publisher=United States Naval Research Laboratory |date=2009-10-08 |accessdate=2012-07-13 |title=Tropical Storm 09L (Grace) Infrared Image Archive |url=http://199.9.2.143/tcdat/tc09/ATL/09L.GRACE/ir/geo/1km_bw/ |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20120713134634/http://199.9.2.143/tcdat/tc09/ATL/09L.GRACE/ir/geo/1km_bw/ |archivedate=2012-07-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

虽然美国国家飓风中心已把格雷斯正式归类为热带气旋，但[[法国气象局|法国气象局]]对此存在异议，并在递交[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]的年度报告中声格雷斯不属热带天气系统。法国气象局称，虽然风暴拥有深层对流和眼状特征，风速还超过每小时95公里，但其总体发展过程更接近于不具备热带天气系统特征的中纬度气旋。<ref name="MFR" />该机构在实际操作中把格雷斯归类为[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Météo-France | date = 2009-10-05 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = La tempête subtropicale Grace, un phénomène rare à nos latitudes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306151416/http://www.meteofrance.fr/?page_id=10320&document_id=21075&portlet_id=42233 | url = http://www.meteofrance.fr/?page_id=10320&document_id=21075&portlet_id=42233 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，还批评美国国家飓风中心是根据[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]和飓风活动逐渐增多的趋势来把风暴作为热带气旋处理<ref name="MFR">{{cite report | author = Météo-France | publisher = [[世界气象组织|World Meteorological Organization]] | date = 2010-02 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Summary of the 2009 Hurricane Season in the French West Indies | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171411/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Meetings/HC32/documents/Doc4.2-1_MeteoFrance_FWI.doc | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no | format = [[DOC格式|DOC]] | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Meetings/HC32/documents/Doc4.2-1_MeteoFrance_FWI.doc }}</ref>。

== 影响和纪录 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Grace_cloudy_skies.jpg|thumb]]
气象机构将位于亚速尔群岛的格雷斯归类成热带气旋后，部分岛屿出现小雨和强风。[[蓬塔德尔加达|蓬塔德尔加达]]测得时速71公里的阵风<ref>{{cite web | author = Resident of Ponta Delgada, Azores | publisher = Weather Underground | date =2009-10-04| accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Weather History for Ponta Delgada, Azores: October 4 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150911050759/http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/LPPD/2009/10/4/DailyHistory.html | url = https://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/LPPD/2009/10/4/DailyHistory.html | archivedate = 2015-09-11 }}</ref>。10月6日同锋面天气系统融合期间，格雷斯的外围[[雨带|雨带]]在[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]部分地区产生狂风暴雨，导致部分街道被淹，估计海拔略高的地点阵风时速超过80公里<ref>{{cite news | author = André Ferreira | publisher = Cofina Media | date = 2009-10-07 | accessdate = 2012-02-22 | title = 'Grace' traz vento e chuva até sexta | archivedate = 2012-02-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120222222701/http://www.cmjornal.xl.pt/noticia.aspx?contentid=0E83C425-359B-4770-8267-FCD767E054D9&channelid=00000009-0000-0000-0000-000000000009 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.cmjornal.xl.pt/noticia.aspx?contentid=0E83C425-359B-4770-8267-FCD767E054D9&channelid=00000009-0000-0000-0000-000000000009 }}</ref>。

由于气旋抵达英国时移动速度相对较快，因此该国的降雨量并不高。爱尔兰的[[科克_(爱尔兰)|科克]]降下30毫米雨量，测得的持续风速只达到每小时37公里<ref>{{cite news |author=Resident of Cork, Ireland |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20130105083749/http://www.wunderground.com/history/station/03955/2009/10/6/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA |archivedate=2013-01-05 |publisher=Weather Underground |date=2009-10-06 |accessdate=2016-04-19 |title=Weather History for Cork, Ireland: October 6, 2009 |url=https://www.wunderground.com/history/station/03955/2009/10/6/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA }}</ref>，[[韦克斯福德|韦克斯福德]]降下48毫米雨量，是该国降水最多的所在<ref>{{cite news | author = Tiffany Curnick | work = Press Association Mediapoint | date = 2009-10-08 | title = Grace Not Typically Tropical, But Parma The Real Deal}}</ref>。[[威尔士|威尔士]]近海的一个浮标测得时速66公里的持续风速，达到热带风暴标准下限<ref>{{cite web | author = Maritime | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2009-10-06 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Weather History for Cork, Ireland: 星期二, 十月 6, 2009 | url = https://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/EICK/2009/10/6/DailyHistory.html?req_city=Roches+Point&req_state=&req_statename=%E6%84%9B%E7%88%BE%E8%98%AD&reqdb.zip=00000&reqdb.magic=1&reqdb.wmo=03952 | archive-date = 2016-10-26 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161026210643/https://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/EICK/2009/10/6/DailyHistory.html?req_city=Roches+Point&req_state=&req_statename=%E6%84%9B%E7%88%BE%E8%98%AD&reqdb.zip=00000&reqdb.magic=1&reqdb.wmo=03952 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。10月6日晚，格雷斯的残留进入威尔士陆地上空，在当地产生狂风暴雨<ref>{{cite web |publisher=MetCheck |archivedate=2009-10-07 |date=2009-10-07 |accessdate=2009-10-07 |title=Fine For Many But Rain In South |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.metcheck.com/V40/UK/HOME/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5kLx7H4gB?url=http://www.metcheck.com/V40/UK/HOME/ }}</ref>。英国的最高降雨量为49毫米<ref>{{cite news | publisher = BBC Weather | date = 2009-10-07 | accessdate = 2009-10-11 | title = Review of UK weather on 06/10/09 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/weather/hi/uk_reviews/newsid_8294000/8294353.stm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20091011160216/http://news.bbc.co.uk/weather/hi/uk_reviews/newsid_8294000/8294353.stm | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2009-10-11 }}</ref>。呼号“{{lang|en|A8PI5}}”的“卡斯蒂略船长号”船只于10月5日在风暴中心以南约180公里洋面测得每小时72公里的持续风速<ref name="TCR" />。格雷斯的残留湿气还对另一个更强烈的气旋推波助澜，产生61毫米降水，在比利时部分地区引发洪灾<ref>{{cite news | publisher = Météo Belgique | date = 2009-10-08 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Flash du 8 octobre 2009 : Pluies orageuses | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308145652/http://meteobelgique.be/communaute/1388-flash-du-8-octobre-2009-pluies-orageuses.html | url = http://www.meteobelgique.be/communaute/1388-flash-du-8-octobre-2009-pluies-orageuses.html }}</ref>。

气象部门在实际操作中直到风暴进行至北纬41.2°时才将其归类为热带风暴，格雷斯至此成功有纪录以来形成位置纬度最高的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]之一，仅次于[[1988年大西洋飓风季|1988年]]的[[1988年大西洋飓风季#热带风暴阿尔贝托|热带风暴阿尔贝托]]<ref name="JeffM" /><ref name="HURDAT" />。不过，气象机构之后经重新分析认定，格雷斯成为热带风暴的时间比初步预计要早12小时，所以位置应该南移至北纬38.5°<ref name="TCR" />。风暴还打破[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年]]时[[飓风文斯|飓风文斯]]所创纪录，至今仍是形成位置最偏东北方向的北大西洋热带气旋<ref name="JeffM" /><ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Specialists Unit | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2016-04-19 | title = Easy to Read HURDAT 1851–2009 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html }}</ref>。

美国国家飓风中心在针对格雷斯发布的热带气旋报告中自承预报工作做得一塌糊涂。10月1日，该机构在首度提及格雷斯的前身低气压区时就预计系统不会发展成热带或亚热带气旋，并且此后三天的热带天气展望中根本没有涉及这一天气系统，直到将其归类为热带风暴前不久才再度提及。这种情况的出现主要是因为风暴所在位置相对偏远，缺乏有效观测数据。<ref name="TCR" />

